OL,6,GThis must have been an exhausting
OL,7,Gweek for BBC One and Two playout
OL,8,Gteams. I've almost lost count of the
OL,9,Gnumber of last minute scheduling
OL,10,Gchanges caused by Wimbledon.
OL,12,FDelays to news bulletins and extended
OL,13,Fcoverage on One had knock on effects
OL,14,Fto Two. Several potential scenarios
OL,15,Fwere worked out.
OL,17,FThis is exactly why live presentation
OL,18,Fis so important for "reactive"
OL,19,Fchannels. Sport and live events can
OL,20,Ftake unpredictable turns.
OL,3,CThe important role of Presentation in
OL,4,Cmanaging "reactive" BBC channels
