OL,6,FImagine cutting off Andy Murray at a
OL,7,Fkey point simply to hit a junction.
OL,8,FImagine if Wednesday's royal ceremony
OL,9,Ffrom Edinburgh had fallen off the air.
OL,11,FBut what about normal live programmes
OL,12,Fkeeping to time?
OL,14,FPart of the skill with live
OL,15,Fbroadcasting is to bring a programme
OL,16,Fout on time. Sometimes this means
OL,17,Fdropping, shortening or elongating
OL,18,Fitems.
