OL,6,FI can't think of many times this has
OL,7,Factually happened in practice ` at
OL,8,Fleast in ways which are obvious to
OL,9,Fviewers. But Richard Marson's
OL,10,Frecently published biography of
OL,11,Flegendary Blue Peter editor Biddy
OL,12,FBaxter contains a gem.
OL,14,FOne Monday in February 1986, disaster
OL,15,Fstruck in the Blue Peter gallery. The
OL,16,FProduction Assistant's stopwatches
OL,17,Ffailed.
OL,19,FThe timings went badly wrong. The
OL,20,Fprogramme was simply taken off the
OL,21,Fair by Pres.
