OL,6,FI find it astounding that this
OL,7,Fhappened.
OL,9,FAny live programme should know it's
OL,10,Fplanned off air time ` the time by
OL,11,Fwhich it absolutely has to finish
OL,12,Fwithout an agreed extension.
OL,14,FThere must have come a point when the
OL,15,Fgallery realised this was going to
OL,16,Fhappen. Were they unable to bring the
OL,17,Fprogramme to a neat and clean if
OL,18,Funexpected conclusion?
