OL,6,FThe 5.35pm network programme ` an
OL,7,FAmerican comedy Charles in Charge `
OL,8,Fhad to run at a certain time to make
OL,9,Fsure the regional trail at 5.59pm got
OL,10,Fto air followed, of course, by the
OL,11,Fclock going into the Six o'Clock
OL,12,FNews. (If the News had been delayed
OL,13,Fby even a few seconds in those
OL,14,Fcircumstances all hell would have
OL,15,Fbroken loose.)
OL,17,FWales and Northern Ireland also
OL,18,Fneeded to opt at 5.35pm for their
OL,19,Fnews programmes.
